  "prompt": "Which is the best plan for international calling in India for people in UAE?",
  "response": "When it comes to international calling plans from the UAE to India, several telecom providers offer competitive options. Here\u2019s a brief overview of some of the best plans available:\n\n1. **Etisalat:**\n   - **Plan:** Freedom India Pack\n   - **Cost:** AED 25\n   - **Inclusions:** 100 minutes to India for 1 month\n   - **Validity:** 30 days\n\n2. **Du:**\n   - **Plan:** Value Pack India\n   - **Cost:** AED 25\n   - **Inclusions:** Unlimited minutes to India for 7 days\n   - **Validity:** 7 days\n\n3. **Lyca Mobile:**\n   - **Plan:** India Plan S\n   - **Cost:** AED 20\n   - **Inclusions:** 1000 minutes to India for 30 days\n   - **Validity:** 30 days\n\n4. **VOIP Services:**\n   - Services like Skype, WhatsApp, and Viber can be cost-effective for international calling. They often offer plans that can be more economical than traditional telecom services, especially for longer calls.\n\n**Recommendation:**\n- If you prefer a traditional telecom service and need a monthly plan, **Lyca Mobile\u2019s India Plan S** seems to offer the best value with 1000 minutes for AED 20.\n- If you need unlimited calls for a shorter period, **Du\u2019s Value Pack India** for AED 25 gives you unlimited minutes for 7 days.\n\nIt\u2019s always a good idea to check the latest offers directly from the providers, as plans can change and special promotions may be available.",
